{"id":23596,"date":"2024-11-13T19:55:04","date_gmt":"2024-11-13T14:25:04","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/?p=23596"},"modified":"2025-07-04T14:32:13","modified_gmt":"2025-07-04T09:02:13","slug":"master-data-management-strategies","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-management-strategies\/","title":{"rendered":"Master Data Management Strategies"},"content":{"rendered":"\t\t<div data-elementor-type=\"wp-post\" data-elementor-id=\"23596\" class=\"elementor elementor-23596\" data-elementor-post-type=\"post\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ff4b500 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ff4b500\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7e3697bb elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7e3697bb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-pm-slice=\"1 1 []\">Master Data Management (MDM) has become an indispensable capability for large enterprises seeking operational efficiency, compliance, and cross-functional transparency. As global businesses scale, the complexity of supply chains, vendor ecosystems, product portfolios, and customer touchpoints increases\u2014making clean, consistent, and governed master data a cornerstone for success.<\/p><p>This article offers an in-depth, technical roadmap on developing effective MDM strategies, covering architecture, data cleansing, governance, enrichment, tooling, and long-term scalability. It blends conceptual depth with practical tactics, including examples from real-world implementations across domains such as Materials, Vendor, Customer, Equipment, and Services Master Data.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4a5d4c8e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4a5d4c8e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f3ea670 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f3ea670\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Master Data Management Plan<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e9bebce e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e9bebce\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eda690d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"eda690d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Large corporations typically rely on a master database for various business-centric processes to enable seamless operational execution and visibility across departments, silos, functions, and, to foster a wider organizational level co-operation.\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">While the idea of a Centralized Data Repository and a &#8220;Golden Record&#8221; that represents a complete source of truth has been in existence since a long time, novel data cleansing and master data governance practices have also been deployed by several technology companies globally.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Similarly, consolidation of production efforts and increasing complexity in supply chains globally have also resulted in novel issues that Master Data Professionals are in dire need to address.<\/span><\/p><p data-start=\"587\" data-end=\"811\">Without a centralized mechanism to manage and synchronize this data, several challenges emerge:<\/p><ul data-start=\"890\" data-end=\"1240\"><li data-start=\"890\" data-end=\"968\"><p data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"968\"><strong data-start=\"892\" data-end=\"917\">Redundant procurement<\/strong> caused by duplicate or incomplete material records<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"969\" data-end=\"1041\"><p data-start=\"971\" data-end=\"1041\"><strong data-start=\"971\" data-end=\"999\">Delayed order processing<\/strong> due to mismatched vendor or customer data<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1042\" data-end=\"1151\"><p data-start=\"1044\" data-end=\"1151\"><strong data-start=\"1044\" data-end=\"1064\">Compliance risks<\/strong> tied to inaccurate or missing regulatory fields (e.g., TIN, tax codes, certifications)<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1152\" data-end=\"1240\"><p data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1240\"><strong data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1180\">Reporting inaccuracies<\/strong> that undermine strategic planning and financial forecasting<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-993f8ba e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"993f8ba\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7609903 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"7609903\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>By addressing data quality and governance at the root, MDM empowers enterprise-wide transformation\u2014from digital supply chains and AI-driven analytics to customer 360 initiatives and ESG compliance.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db019e5 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"db019e5\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7f990fa elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7f990fa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Issues with a Master Database<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-756724c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"756724c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-032d091 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"032d091\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>&#8220;While each master data domain &#8211; be it material, vendor, customer, or asset\u2014has its own complexities and operational nuances, every effective Master Data Management strategy is anchored in two foundational principles: structured domain definition and disciplined data governance. The following strategies build on this foundation to ensure consistency, scalability, and trust in enterprise data.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2e7eea4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2e7eea4\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-70d0083 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"70d0083\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Scope of Master Database<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-87f38d3 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"87f38d3\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-07972c2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"07972c2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"434\">Master data isn&#8217;t just one type of data\u2014it spans across many core domains like customer, supplier, product, asset, and location data. To manage it effectively:<\/p><ul data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"881\"><li data-start=\"435\" data-end=\"648\"><p data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"648\"><strong data-start=\"437\" data-end=\"516\">What constitutes \u201cmaster data\u201d for your organization.<\/strong><br \/>For example, in a manufacturing company, products and assets might be primary; in retail, customer and location data are crucial.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"649\" data-end=\"881\"><p data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"881\"><strong data-start=\"651\" data-end=\"685\">Each domain has its own schema<\/strong>, attributes, and business relevance. A product record might include fields like product category, SKU, and unit of measure, while a customer record may contain address, credit rating, and region.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e905594 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e905594\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"883\" data-end=\"1052\">Defining this scope ensures you&#8217;re not trying to govern every piece of enterprise data &#8211; just the foundational entities that drive transactions, analytics, and compliance.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0a6a6e8 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0a6a6e8\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7ee80ed elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7ee80ed\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Scoping and Structuring Master Data Domains<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ae4be38 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ae4be38\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f849bea elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f849bea\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"722\">One of the most strategic starting points for any MDM initiative is to properly define and structure the enterprise\u2019s master data domains. These domains represent the core entities &#8211; such as materials, vendors, customers, equipment, and services &#8211; that drive day-to-day transactions and long-term business intelligence.<\/p><p data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"722\">Without clear scoping and standardization, downstream initiatives in data governance, cleansing, enrichment, and automation will lack cohesion and scalability.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ec78ed e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"2ec78ed\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-111ab89 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"111ab89\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Common Master Data Domains:<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-db4a1eb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"db4a1eb\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dfcf911 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dfcf911\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<ul><li data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"793\"><p><strong data-start=\"760\" data-end=\"793\">Material (MRO\/Finished Goods): <\/strong>Captures critical procurement and inventory control data\u2014Manufacturer Part Number (MPN), manufacturer name, detailed item descriptions, Unit of Measure (UoM), commodity classification, and material group. This directly supports BOM accuracy, spend analytics, and sourcing efficiency.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"794\" data-end=\"815\"><p data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"815\"><strong data-start=\"796\" data-end=\"815\">Vendor\/Supplier:\u00a0<\/strong>Includes Taxpayer Identification Number (TIN), addresses, banking details, payment terms, contact information, and compliance documentation. A clean vendor master is essential for risk mitigation, payment processing, and onboarding automation.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"816\" data-end=\"830\"><p data-start=\"818\" data-end=\"830\"><strong data-start=\"818\" data-end=\"830\">Customer:\u00a0<\/strong>Contains asset ID, serial and model numbers, manufacturer details, installation\/commissioning dates, warranty status, and associated spares. This supports maintenance strategies and predictive analytics in asset-intensive industries.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"853\"><p data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"853\"><strong data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"853\">Equipment\/Assets:\u00a0<\/strong>Contains asset ID, serial and model numbers, manufacturer details, installation\/commissioning dates, warranty status, and associated spares. This supports maintenance strategies and predictive analytics in asset-intensive industries.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"831\" data-end=\"853\"><p data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"853\"><strong>Services: <\/strong>Defines services offered or procured, with attributes such as service category, SLA terms, rate structure, applicable geographies, and contract duration. Structured service data enables better vendor governance and cost controls.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6750d1a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6750d1a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d51a8b8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d51a8b8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Modeling Interrelationships and Hierarchies:<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c1fc499 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c1fc499\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef11794 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ef11794\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"2646\" data-end=\"2753\">Strategic MDM requires modeling not just the domains but also how they relate to one another. For instance:<\/p><ul data-start=\"2754\" data-end=\"3012\"><li data-start=\"2754\" data-end=\"2818\"><p data-start=\"2756\" data-end=\"2818\">Linking <strong data-start=\"2764\" data-end=\"2788\">materials to vendors<\/strong> establishes sourcing clarity.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2819\" data-end=\"2906\"><p data-start=\"2821\" data-end=\"2906\">Mapping <strong data-start=\"2829\" data-end=\"2863\">equipment to service providers<\/strong> enables preventive maintenance automation.<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"2907\" data-end=\"3012\"><p data-start=\"2909\" data-end=\"3012\">Structuring <strong data-start=\"2921\" data-end=\"2952\">customer &gt; region &gt; account<\/strong> hierarchies supports accurate credit control and analytics.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f2bd6b4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f2bd6b4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"3014\" data-end=\"3155\">These interdependencies are critical for driving process standardization across procurement, finance, operations, and supply chain functions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-85ca90e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"85ca90e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f458171 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f458171\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Domain interrelationships\u2014such as which vendors supply which materials, or which equipment is serviced by which contractors\u2014should also be explicitly modeled.<\/p><p>Establishing robust domain hierarchies (e.g., customer &gt; region &gt; account) and relationships (e.g., material\u2013vendor linkage) ensures high data integrity, streamlined reporting, and seamless integration across transactional systems like ERP, CRM, and EAM.<\/p><p>Clear and consistent domain modeling not only ensures internal alignment but also provides scalability, better data stewardship, and compatibility with downstream systems.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-94df060 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"94df060\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19c539e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"19c539e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Master Data Cleansing <\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-de8d825 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"de8d825\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-09df91d elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"09df91d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>This entails a thorough &#8220;<strong>Harmonization<\/strong>&#8221; of the legacy master data records. Data deduplication, structuring, standardization and enrichment are key aspects that are covered here.\u00a0\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8a26075 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8a26075\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Data Deduplication is fairly straightforward. Overtime, any business process leads to duplicate entries in the system. A database riddled with duplicate entries is unlikely to provide full visibility into the business requirements and all duplicate records need to be identified, consolidated and weeded out of the master database, to make it more &#8220;reliable&#8221;.<\/p><p>In order to harness the various benefits of having a reliable master data, every data record should be as exhaustive as possible to make the most of the database.<\/p><p>This is particularly true for key data points that we will be covering further. For example; a customer master data record should ideally have &#8220;Email address&#8221; and &#8220;Phone Number&#8221; to ensure greater operational ease.\u00a0<\/p><p>Generally, most master data management solutions worth their salt offer some kind of enrichment solutions either natively through their own database or through third party solutions.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-10b0a35 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"10b0a35\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3144611 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3144611\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Identifying Duplicates<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-68a9a10 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"68a9a10\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e0aca1a elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e0aca1a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Generally speaking, most master databases have a relatively identifiable &#8220;unique key&#8221; even though they may or may not have been configured in the system. Exact match duplicates can easily be identified by running a duplicate check on any modern database solutions or even on something as rudimentary as an Excel Sheet.<\/p><p>Some examples of &#8220;properties&#8221; or &#8220;fields&#8221; that can be used to identify duplicates for different MDM types are listed below.\u00a0<\/p><ul><li><p>Tax Identification Number in the case of Vendor Master &#8211;\u00a0<\/p><\/li><li><p>Manufacturer Part Number in the case of Materials Master Data<\/p><\/li><li><p>Email address in the case of customer master data<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p>This are generally the easiest to identify and weed them out of the system and they&#8217;re generally referred to as L1 duplicates.<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">L2 duplicates, on the other hand, are far more difficult to identify and rely on multiple datapoints and technologies to be identified\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Fuzzy matching, for example, is a time-tested method of identifying similarities in a string of characters within the same data base.<\/span><\/p><p>Most modern database solutions support &#8220;Fuzzy Logic&#8221; to identify potential duplicates, Even something as rudimentary as Microsoft <a href=\"https:\/\/www.microsoft.com\/en-in\/download\/details.aspx?id=15011\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Excel has a add-on for Fuzzy Matching data<\/a> in two different columns.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c5831e4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c5831e4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Far more modern master data solutions, like Harmonize\u00a9 (the software we&#8217;ve built internally at Appfinity) leverage LLMs and specifically trained Machine Learning Models to &#8220;Understand&#8221; the data in different master data records and score them on the likelihood of them being duplicates.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-eb7e90a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"eb7e90a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e98a74d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"e98a74d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"377\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4-1024x482.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-23911\" alt=\"Harmonize Data De-Duplication\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4-1024x482.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4-300x141.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4-768x362.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4-150x71.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Harmonize-4.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bdab18f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"bdab18f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3ff8dca elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3ff8dca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Attribute Extraction <\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ecad0c7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ecad0c7\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e773ec4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e773ec4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Reliable master data records typically have information arranged systematically into different fields to ensure scalability and automations work seamlessly. More importantly, structured information invariably leads to better decision making.<\/p><p>However, in many cases, master records are unstructured &#8211; here are few examples below.<\/p><ul><li><p>\u00a0MRO Material records typically have a part short description or a long description wherein attributes specific to that product are stuffed in the description<\/p><\/li><li><p>A Customer Master Record typically has a &#8220;long address&#8221; or &#8220;contact details&#8221; wherein the email address or the phone number is stuffed within the same record<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">These descriptions are typically written in an unstructured manner, data from these open-ended cells can be extracted and mapped to the relevant fields to ensure completeness and accuracy of the master data in line with the database schema<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c4da95c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c4da95c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37c19f4 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"37c19f4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"363\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction-1024x464.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-24196\" alt=\"Attribute Extraction\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction-1024x464.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction-300x136.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction-768x348.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction-150x68.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Attribute-Extraction.png 1351w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a25a03e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"a25a03e\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-82bc883 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"82bc883\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Data Enrichment<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b347a0f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b347a0f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dd66410 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dd66410\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The central theme of MDM solutions, in general, is to have one &#8220;master record&#8221; or &#8220;golden record&#8221; that acts as a single source of truth for decision making across functions and seniorities within an organization<\/p><p><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\">This single source of &#8220;truth&#8221; should ideally have &#8220;Complete Information&#8221; to enable this decision making<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">This is why most data input systems have a &#8220;required fields&#8221; that are mandatory to be filled out before making an entry\/request\/submission.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Certain other data points may not be mandatory per-se but are <b>Good-to-Haves <\/b>and certainly enable faster and better decision making.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Some of these examples are below<\/span><\/p><ul><li><p>It&#8217;s always beneficial to have &#8220;<strong>Address<\/strong>&#8221; or &#8220;<strong>Tax Identification Number<\/strong>&#8221; or &#8220;Parent Organization Information&#8221; in a Vendor Master record<\/p><\/li><li><p>Similarly, it&#8217;s always beneficial to have &#8220;Manufacturer Part Number&#8221; or &#8220;Manufacturer Name&#8221; <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/materials-master-data-management\/\">for Materials Master Data Records<\/a><\/p><\/li><li><p>A Customer Master Data Record can benefit from having datapoints like &#8220;Customer email&#8221; or &#8220;Gender&#8221; mapped correctly to the master data record\u00a0<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d5ca9bd e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d5ca9bd\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24f5941 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"24f5941\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"364\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment-1024x466.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-24195\" alt=\"Data Enrichment\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment-1024x466.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment-300x136.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment-768x349.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment-150x68.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Data-Enrichment.png 1346w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d0a49ce e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"d0a49ce\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5a47e71 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5a47e71\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-management-services\/\">Modern Master Data Management Companies and Software Solutions<\/a> typically have &#8220;Enrichment&#8221; systems in place that leverage internal databases or third part data sources to enrich a database automatically, albeit with some manual reviews required\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f861c76 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"f861c76\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1053dee elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1053dee\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Master Data Governance Strategies<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b111189 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"b111189\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fabb941 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fabb941\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Cleaning and standardizing a Master Database is only part of a puzzle, and a relatively easier one to address.<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">The real challenges that companies face are directly related to putting in place preventive &#8220;Governance&#8221; systems that will do away with the need to repetitively cleansing the legacy master data.<\/span><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ed6f67 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"5ed6f67\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b1522a3 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b1522a3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>One of the more complex challenges in a Master Data Management system is developing and implementing effective data cleansing strategies, which focuses on strategies to enhance data accuracy, consistency, and reliability across your organization.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e28bdd0 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e28bdd0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-40b82a7 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"40b82a7\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Easily one of the tougher pieces to crack in a Master Data Management system are the strategies. We have covered <a href=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/master-data-governance\/\">the basics of Master Data Governance Solutions earlier<\/a>, this piece is more geared towards specific strategies that can be employed for implementing a Master Data Governance.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-65687f7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"65687f7\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e898780 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e898780\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Semantic Search<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ceeb46b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ceeb46b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a5b7353 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a5b7353\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>As <a href=\"https:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/Semantic_search\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">per WikiPedia<\/a>, Semantic search denotes search with meaning, as distinguished from lexical search where the search engine looks for literal matches of the query words or variants of them, without understanding the overall meaning of the query.\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3e45c5c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3e45c5c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca1ee13 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ca1ee13\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Technology powerhouses like Google heavily rely on similar Semantic Search technologies and language models to retrieve information from their databases of websites.<\/p><p>Similarly, Master Data Governance solutions also leverage Semantic Search functionalities to avoid any new data entry request from being &#8220;Duplicated&#8221; in the system. Modern data governance solutions, like Integrity, a product built in-house by Appfinity, also leverages Artificial Intelligence to &#8220;Understand&#8221; every given master data record and highlight potential duplicates before they are added into the system<\/p><p>With AI-first processes making its way into Master Data Management pretty rapidly, companies are increasingly seeing its immense benefits and the value it drives as far as operational ease and accuracy is concerned.\u00a0<\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Most enterprise-grade ERPs like SAP and Oracle tend to have native data governance frameworks in place but they tend to be quite rigid, not too intuitive in terms of UI and are generally quite resource intensive to configure as per the exact specifications for every client.<\/span><\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7c9439a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7c9439a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3f32c8 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"a3f32c8\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"376\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search-1024x481.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-23895\" alt=\"Semantic Search\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search-1024x481.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search-300x141.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search-768x360.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search-150x70.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-Semantic-Search.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-301536f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"301536f\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8c4f4ff elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"8c4f4ff\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Access Controls<\/h4>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1d87a5a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1d87a5a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-37ec190 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"37ec190\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">As most data-governance Gurus would claim, Master Data Management is not a discipline that exists in Silos, its policies and protocols are defined both top-down and bottom-up, and is generally not a one-time activity but a continuously improving process\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">Defining the right permissions and approval systems right from &#8220;requester&#8221; all the way up to the master data administrator is a policy-level decision that will need to be configured across functions within an enterprise.\u00a0<\/span><\/p><p><span style=\"color: var( --e-global-color-text ); font-family: var( --e-global-typography-text-font-family ), Sans-serif; text-align: var(--text-align);\">These access levels are typically something like this<\/span><\/p><ol><li><p>Operational User<\/p><\/li><li><p>Data Architect<\/p><\/li><li><p>Data Steward<\/p><\/li><li><p>Data Custodian<\/p><\/li><li><p>Data Owner<\/p><\/li><\/ol>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d942e0e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d942e0e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Each of these users have their own access-levels for editing, creating, updating or approving master data records to ensure organization-wide compliance and accountability\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-56b336b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"56b336b\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8b14841 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"8b14841\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"346\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity-1024x443.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-24197\" alt=\"Workflow Framework\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity-1024x443.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity-300x130.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity-768x332.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity-150x65.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Workflow-Approvals-Integrity.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-963d3a7 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"963d3a7\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2fee524 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"2fee524\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Data Quality Framework<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-84b3fc4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"84b3fc4\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-000f7b2 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"000f7b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>A robust <strong>Data Quality Framework<\/strong> is a key strategy for ensuring that master data remains reliable and consistent across the organization. Establishing a clear set of data quality standards and metrics helps organizations monitor and continuously improve data accuracy, completeness, consistency, and timeliness.<\/p><p><strong>Key Components of a Data Quality Framework<\/strong>:<\/p><ul><li><p><strong>Data Profiling<\/strong>: This involves analyzing data to identify anomalies, inconsistencies, and gaps. Regular data profiling helps organizations understand the current state of their data and assess the impact of data quality issues.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Data Quality Rules<\/strong>: Organizations should define and enforce specific data quality rules, such as ensuring all customer records include email addresses or that product records have a valid manufacturer part number.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Continuous Monitoring<\/strong>: Monitoring data quality on an ongoing basis ensures that issues are detected early. Automated tools can be implemented to flag out-of-compliance data or deviations from established quality standards.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Data Quality KPIs<\/strong>: Key Performance Indicators (KPIs) like accuracy, completeness, consistency, and timeliness help track the effectiveness of the data quality strategy over time.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e827945 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e827945\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Example<\/strong>: Implementing an automated data profiling tool that flags records that do not meet established data quality rules, allowing data stewards to quickly address issues and improve the quality of the master data.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fe209be e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fe209be\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-197b627 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"197b627\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Master Data Automation<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33d8bbc e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"33d8bbc\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca410c6 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ca410c6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Automating various aspects of Master Data Management helps reduce manual errors, streamline workflows, and accelerate data processing. Automation tools can significantly improve data accuracy, consistency, and the speed at which data is integrated and maintained across systems.<\/p><p><strong>Key Areas for Automation<\/strong>:<\/p><ul><li><p><strong>Data Entry and Validation<\/strong>: Automatically validate incoming data entries against predefined rules and standards, ensuring that data is accurate and complete before being added to the master database.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Data Reconciliation<\/strong>: Automate the reconciliation of data from different systems to identify discrepancies and ensure consistency across databases.<\/p><\/li><li><p><strong>Workflow Automation<\/strong>: Automate data approval workflows, notifications, and change requests to streamline the process of updating master data.<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e98530e elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e98530e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p><strong>Example<\/strong>: A pharmaceutical company uses an automated solution to validate and enrich supplier data based on third-party databases, ensuring that all vendor records are complete and up-to-date without manual intervention.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3d2dacb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3d2dacb\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3aefe9d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"3aefe9d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"347\" src=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2-1024x444.png\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-23891\" alt=\"Data Validation\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2-1024x444.png 1024w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2-300x130.png 300w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2-768x333.png 768w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2-150x65.png 150w, https:\/\/www.verdantis.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/11\/Appfinity-MDG-2.png 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" title=\"\">\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8da7b2d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8da7b2d\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d93f5b5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d93f5b5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Implement Scalable, Integrated MDM Platforms<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c5bd15 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"9c5bd15\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc45bfd elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"fc45bfd\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"169\" data-end=\"397\">Avoid treating Master Data Management as an isolated IT initiative. The right MDM platform must support cross-functional use cases while enabling seamless integration across your enterprise systems. A robust MDM solution should:<\/p><ul data-start=\"399\" data-end=\"931\"><li data-start=\"399\" data-end=\"508\"><p data-start=\"401\" data-end=\"508\">Deliver <strong data-start=\"409\" data-end=\"439\">domain-specific governance<\/strong> out of the box for materials, vendors, customers, assets, and more<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"509\" data-end=\"624\"><p data-start=\"511\" data-end=\"624\">Enable users to <strong data-start=\"527\" data-end=\"560\">create, modify, and syndicate<\/strong> master data across ERP, CRM, PLM, and other connected systems<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"625\" data-end=\"747\"><p data-start=\"627\" data-end=\"747\">Support <strong data-start=\"635\" data-end=\"655\">open integration<\/strong> with third-party tools, APIs, and data services for validation, enrichment, or onboarding<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"748\" data-end=\"852\"><p data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"852\">Facilitate <strong data-start=\"761\" data-end=\"797\">advanced analytics and reporting<\/strong> to assess data quality, compliance, and usage trends<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"931\"><p data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"931\"><strong data-start=\"855\" data-end=\"877\">Scale effortlessly<\/strong> with enterprise growth and evolving data complexity<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5e90079 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5e90079\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"1174\">Selecting a future-ready, AI-augmented MDM platform ensures longevity, adaptability, and value realization across your digital initiatives.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c991d1c e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c991d1c\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7b63f08 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7b63f08\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Establish a Continuous Improvement Loop<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fda2449 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fda2449\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5c5e062 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5c5e062\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"1132\" data-end=\"1330\">Master Data Management is an <strong data-start=\"1161\" data-end=\"1180\">ongoing process<\/strong>, not a one-time fix. To maintain trust in your single source of truth (SSOT), organizations must adopt a continuous improvement model. This includes:<\/p><ul data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1742\"><li data-start=\"1332\" data-end=\"1427\"><p data-start=\"1334\" data-end=\"1427\"><strong data-start=\"1334\" data-end=\"1361\">Monitoring data quality<\/strong> in real time through profiling dashboards and rule-based alerts<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1428\" data-end=\"1530\"><p data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1530\"><strong data-start=\"1430\" data-end=\"1452\">Refreshing records<\/strong> regularly using enrichment feeds, third-party APIs, and user feedback loops<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1652\"><p data-start=\"1533\" data-end=\"1652\"><strong data-start=\"1533\" data-end=\"1567\">Reviewing governance workflows<\/strong> to adapt to changing business needs, regulatory requirements, or domain expansions<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"1653\" data-end=\"1742\"><p data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1742\"><strong data-start=\"1655\" data-end=\"1698\">Repeating quality and compliance checks<\/strong> on a defined schedule to avoid regression<\/p><\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1b0cd37 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"1b0cd37\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"1174\">Without periodic validation and realignment, even the most well-structured MDM implementation can deteriorate\u2014leading to misaligned systems, duplicated records, and poor decision-making. A resilient MDM strategy builds data health into the business fabric.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e638e22 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e638e22\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-33fb2d0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"33fb2d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Conclusion<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-fc4170a e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"fc4170a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6de48cf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6de48cf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"194\" data-end=\"388\">Master Data Management is not a one-time initiative\u2014it\u2019s a sustained, enterprise-wide discipline that aligns technology, people, and processes to create a reliable, scalable data foundation.<\/p><p data-start=\"390\" data-end=\"499\">To build and maintain this foundation, organizations must embrace a comprehensive MDM strategy that includes:<\/p><ul data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"857\"><li data-start=\"500\" data-end=\"578\"><p data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"578\"><strong data-start=\"502\" data-end=\"527\">Cleansing legacy data<\/strong> through deduplication, enrichment, and structuring<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"579\" data-end=\"670\"><p data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"670\"><strong data-start=\"581\" data-end=\"608\">Establishing governance<\/strong> with semantic search, access controls, and approval workflows<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"671\" data-end=\"749\"><p data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"749\"><strong data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"702\">Automating data processes<\/strong> to reduce manual errors and improve efficiency<\/p><\/li><li data-start=\"750\" data-end=\"857\"><p data-start=\"752\" data-end=\"857\"><strong data-start=\"752\" data-end=\"796\">Selecting scalable, AI-enabled platforms<\/strong> that support real-time integration and semantic intelligence<\/p><\/li><\/ul><p data-start=\"1176\" data-end=\"1323\">\u00a0<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9f3f67c elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9f3f67c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-start=\"859\" data-end=\"1174\">As AI and real-time data integration become central to enterprise operations, MDM is transforming from a back-office IT concern into a core business capability. Trusted master data underpins everything\u2014from digital transformation and predictive analytics to operational efficiency and regulatory compliance.<\/p><p data-start=\"1176\" data-end=\"1323\">By investing in robust MDM strategies today, organizations can ensure data integrity, agility, and competitive advantage\u2014now and in the future.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Master Data Management (MDM) has become an indispensable capability for large enterprises seeking operational efficiency, compliance, and cross-functional transparency. As global businesses scale, the complexity of supply chains, vendor ecosystems, product portfolios, and customer touchpoints increases\u2014making clean, consistent, and governed master data a cornerstone for success. This article offers an in-depth, technical roadmap on developing [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":6,"featured_media":23944,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[64],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-23596","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-blog"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.verdant